''' <summary>
''' Provides an ArcMap Command with functionality to
''' Construct a Spiral-Curve-Spiral transition feature.
''' These features are common in Highways and freeways.
''' </summary>
''' <remarks><seealso cref="SCS_tool"/></remarks>


